episodes.title: The Messiah: meet the Australian man who says he's Jesus and his followers | 7NEWS Spotlight
episodes.description:
In this special worldwide investigation, meet the self-proclaimed Messiah whose devoted disciples believe he walked this earth 2,000 years ago. One of the world’s foremost experts on cults, Reverand David Milliken goes inside Alan John Miller’s isolated Queensland compound, where he’s preparing his followers, including children, for the apocalyptic end of the world. This story originally aired in 2011.
